songkick_response.displayName: SOULFUL SOUNDS at 2440 Victory Park Ln (December 11, 2016)

bandsintown_response.description:
Join us for an evening of great music at the luxurious W Dallas Victory Hotel and Residences,  located in downtown Dallas, TX. Start the evening off with the smooth sounds of DJ Erick starting at 6pm. Sit back and enjoy your dinner with the purchase of a dinner package while listening DJ Erick take you on a musical ride back through the years. Or just relax and enjoy a cocktail of your choice from the elegant bar during our dinner/happy hour from 6 to 8 pm. 
Showtime!!!!!
*Comedian Edwin Douglas will be bringing the laughs and keeping the party going. Coming off a great show opening for Tamela Mann, Edwin is ready to make your sides hurt.
*Platinum recording artist Quindon Tarver (When Doves Cry remake and Romeo and Juliet Soundtrack) will be showcasing his talents in front of the packed house. This brother has a voice that will make you get out of your seats. He can show you better than I can tell you.
*Will Foraker is going to blow you away with his vocals and keyboard skills. When you hear him sing you'll definitely want to hear more. Your going to feel like you've known him for years due to his skills to make the audience feel like they're apart of the show.
*DFW's own Ti-Shara is going to make you fall in love when you hear her voice. With the talent to sing any genre of music she's going to take you on a musical journey. One that you will never forget.
*I like to call her my million dollar baby because this young lady can sannnngggg.... Bringing a sound that's going make you shake your head and stomp your feet. Tamyra Butler is going to make a musical believer out of you when she hits the stage. You can thank me later. :-) 
This is going to be a night to remember so get your tickets now. 
After party to follow at the Living Room Bar located on the main floor. 
$20.00 general admission 
$40.00 general admission and dinner. (Buffet style dinner)
bandsintown_response.title: Soulful Sounds @ 2440 Victory Park Ln in Dallas, TX
